<div class="Sections">
	<section class="Section">
		<div class="Manchet">
			<h1><small>Permanently</small> delete <small>{{model.title}}</small></h1>
			<p>Delete your channel from Radio4000.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="Container Container--full">
			<div class="Grid">
				<article class="Grid-cell">
					{{channel-card channel=model}}
				</article>
				<article class="Grid-cell Grid-cell--double">
					<p>Deleting your radio channel will result in:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>Deletion of all information and music saved in your radio.</li>
						<li>Deletion of all radios you saved as favorites.</li>
						<li>Your radio will therefore be inaccessible to any other user.</li>
					</ul>

					<p>Note:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>
							This action does not <a href="https://support.internet4000.com/radio4000/#how-to-delete-my-radio4000-account" target="_blank">delete your Radio4000 account</a>.
						</li>
						<li>You can always create a new radio later.</li>
					</ul>

					<div class="BtnGroup">
						<a href="{{href-to 'channel.index' model}}" class="Btn">Keep my channel online</a>
						<button disabled={{isDeleting}} class="Btn Btn--danger" {{action 'deleteChannel'}}>
							{{#if isDeleting}}
								Deletingâ€¦
							{{else}}
								Delete channel (for real)
							{{/if}}
						</button>
					</div>
				</article>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</div>
